  <p>Apple have released a preview (now onto it's second iteration) of Xcode 4 - a brand new interface for Cocoa development that seeks to unify them into a single application and have advertised it as being intelligent enough to help you write better code.</p> 
  <blockquote cite="https://developer.apple.com/technologies/tools/whats-new.html" title="What's new in Xcode 4"> 
    <p>The Xcode IDE understands your projects every detail, identifies mistakes in both syntax and logic, and will even fix your code for you. Quite simply, Xcode 4 will help you write better code.</p> 
